{"tid":1883772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 鄭泳舜赴日博攞尾彩？ - 李八方","createTime":"2020-02-17T07:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T02:04:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99e782e9c320192222c2efd94f7153063df7e77e","tid":1883772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/2VU7KZBJECFNLOOE5DNHFWVE4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2F2VU7KZBJECFNLOOE5DNHFWVE4A%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=b2a44af4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2F2VU7KZBJECFNLOOE5DNHFWVE4A%2F&h=55ea66d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/2VU7KZBJECFNLOOE5DNHFWVE4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n鄭泳舜赴日博攞尾彩？ - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200217/large/1581871462_a9b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200217%2Flarge%2F1581871462_a9b9.jpg&h=7110bd3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭泳舜<br />\n<br />\n「鑽石公主號」喺日本橫濱被隔離，上面嘅香港乘客一直話港府冇乜幫到佢哋。搞咗一輪，政府終於決定派包機接佢哋返香港，就喺呢個時候，一直話幫船上港人嘅民建聯立法會議員鄭泳舜，突然帶晒物資飛去日本，話要做支援，但好多網民都問，點解鄭泳舜上星期開記招關注事件嘅時候，唔立即飛去日本，而係知件事就快解決先去？<br />\n<br />\n落機急見官員<br />\n<br />\n仲有網民質疑，𠵱家日本政府封咗隻船，即使港府派包機接港人返嚟，好大機會由碼頭直接去機場，咁鄭泳舜又點見到港人支援呢？不過呢個唔重要，因為鄭泳舜一到日本，立即喺機場同中國駐日本大使館參事官兼總領事詹孔朝交流，話希望日本當局盡快為香港旅客進行病毒檢測，之後又見埋派去當地入境處人員同駐東京辦人員傾檢疫及包機安排，做晒呢啲工夫畀人睇，第日又可以有光環，話係自己成功爭取喇！"},{"pid":"78eafcc784b5e553ea0a449591ccbe94e07e7c26","tid":1883772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:03:05.000Z","msg":"19號 星期三 18:15 - 19:15 公民廣場流水式集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1885680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1885680</a>"},{"pid":"3f27412e441da9e07a1bb27e9ef2058617ffe759","tid":1883772,"uid":188998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"尾彩任你攞 最緊要人有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}